Item.ДекорацияБезОтладки.Title=Algorithms are not exported. The mode is convenient when algorithm debugging is not required. Algorithms will be executed, but their code is not available for debugging.
Item.ДекорацияКакПроцедуры.Title=Algorithms are exported as separate procedures. When an algorithm is called, the corresponding processing procedure is invoked. See help for mode usage limitations.
Item.ДекорацияПоМестуВызова.Title=Algorithms are exported as integrated code in handlers, i.e. instead of the algorithm call line, the full algorithm code is inserted including nested algorithms. See help for mode usage limitations.
