Item.ПояснениеДекорация.Title=1. After generating the debug module, copy the resulting handlers code to the clipboard.\n2. Open Designer and create a new external data processor. Paste the clipboard contents into the data processor module. Save the data processor.\n3. On the final fourth step, specify the newly created data processor as the data processor with exported handler procedures.\n
